title: Celine Dion & Cher's Feud Erupts Backstage At Billboard Music Awards

meta_data.description: Superstar singers Cher and Celine Dion gave iconic performances last night at the Billboard Music Awards in Las Vegas, but Radar has learned that there was a bitter battle backstage. Find out why!
